  -files/colortail-0.3.0-gcc3.patch, -colortail-0.3.0-r2.ebuild,
  colortail-0.3.0-r3.ebuild:
  Updated HOMEPAGE and SRC_URI for bug 73512; also updated to use
  toolchain-funcs.eclass rather than gcc.eclass.

